# Game UI Rules

This is not a normal website.

## Treat these as hero areas
- Home page = cinematic entry point
- Collection = premium codex / archive
- Deck builder = command center
- Match UI = clarity-first battlefield
- Cards = hero objects, not ordinary panels

## Card UI rules
- cards must feel valuable
- rarity and faction should read instantly
- hover states should feel premium, not gimmicky
- card framing should be consistent
- sizing rhythm must be deliberate

## Layout rules
- sections need clear focal points
- spacing should create authority and calm
- dense information must still scan quickly
- mobile must remain clean and legible

## Modal rules
- modals should feel intentional and premium
- strong framing
- good close affordance
- no messy overflow
